## Overview
The Fin2 SAP FinOps demo application is deployed as a static app on SAP BTP Cloud Foundry using the `staticfile_buildpack`.

## Live URL
https://fin2-app-friendly-wombat-qf.cfapps.eu01-canary.hana.ondemand.com

## Project Files

### `manifest.yml`
```yaml
---
applications:
  - name: fin2-app
    memory: 64M
    disk_quota: 256M
    buildpacks:
      - staticfile_buildpack
    path: dist
    random-route: true
```

### `public/Staticfile`
```
root: .
pushstate: enabled
```
- Located in `public/` folder so Vite copies it to `dist/` on build
- `pushstate: enabled` ensures SPA routing works (all routes serve index.html)

## Deployment Steps

### Build & Package
```bash
npm run build
cd dist && zip -r ../fin2-app.zip .
```

### Deploy via BTP Cockpit
1. Go to your Space → Applications
2. Click "Deploy Application"
3. Upload `fin2-app.zip`
4. Select buildpack: `staticfile_buildpack`
5. Deploy & Start

### Deploy via CF CLI
```bash
cf login -a https://api.cf.<region>.hana.ondemand.com
cf push
```

## Troubleshooting

### Chart.js "bar is not a registered controller" Error
Fixed by adding `BarController` and `LineController` to Chart.js registration:
- `src/components/charts/BarLineChart.jsx`
- `src/pages/Overview/LicenseUtilizationTile.jsx`

### Blank Page / Assets Not Loading
Ensure `Staticfile` is in the `public/` folder (not project root) so it gets copied to `dist/` during build.

## Tech Stack
- React 18 + Vite
- Chart.js for visualizations
- Static hosting (no backend)
- All data is mock/static
